<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  As you can see, you refuted what we were saying, and the way you said it implied we were lying, there is no other way to look at it, plus your tone was insulting and degrading.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
My tone? You can't possibly know what my tone is through text. And if anyone has been throwing the insults and degradition around here it's been you, not me. I stated my oponions and you took personal offence to what I said.<br>
